Name: sign up or login.

description:
The user will have the ability to enter the app by signning up with user name and password.

players: user.

preconditions:
-to login: if the user already signed up.
-the user Will have to meet the registration conditions to signup.

Basic flow:
	1) open the app.
	2) insert username+password.
	3) press login.
	4)

alternate flow:
If the user was not registered, in the login page will be signup option.

exception flow:
if the user insert a wrong password/username, the app will inform the user and won't let him enter.

post conditions:
the user will get into the app.
